        Creates a new Template for the given data
        Parameters:
        templateFile - the TemplateFile pointing to the physical template file.
        name - template name
        unresolvedDestinationPath - path of the destination file
        unresolvedTemplatePath - relative path of the actual file to generate to. Path variables and relocates are not resolved.
        mergeStrategy - for the template
        outputCharset - output charset for the generated contents
